4. Recommended Usage
âœ… Use Geo-DR When:
â€¢ You require namespace continuity (queues/topics)
â€¢ Your system can tolerate message loss in DR scenarios
â€¢ You need a mature, production-grade DR solution
â€¢ You want to keep things simple (no data sync complexity)
âœ… Use Geo-Replication When:
â€¢ You want full message and metadata replication
â€¢ You are okay with preview-level support
â€¢ You need zero-data-loss and active-active/standby DR strategy
â€¢ Youâ€™re building new systems and can tolerate evolving features
 
5. Hybrid DR Strategy (Recommended for Enterprise)
For organizations needing both namespace and message durability, consider combining both approaches:
â€¢ Use Geo-DR for fast alias-based namespace failover
â€¢ Use custom Function Apps or Event Grid to backup and mirror messages between primary and secondary namespaces
â€¢ Optionally: leverage Geo-Replication (once GA) to simplify dual-write logic